- ATH Móvil – Start sending and receiving money transfers from person to person directly from Mi Banco Mobile app. The service works for new and existing ATH móvil customers.
- iPhone 6 and iPhone 6 Plus screen support – The app perfectly adapts to your device’s screen.
- 3D Touch Support.
- Updated Branch and ATM information.

Note: If you need to change the app language you can do it in the phone settings, just look for the MiBanco app in the phone settings, there you can change the language.

- With RETIRO MÓVIL you can withdraw or send cash to anyone, even if the recipient doesn't have a bank account. To cash out, the recipient just needs to download the Mi Banco app and visit an Automatic Teller Machine (ATM) located at one of Banco Popular’s branches with the RETIRO MÓVIL service. It’s that simple!
